<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<sample sampleID="LBg9_00152" version="1.0" type="fixedLength">
<article articleID="LBg9_00152_F001">
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「何とでも思うがよかろう。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">お前も似たようなもの<sampling type="start" />なのだからな」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「無礼を申すと許さんぞ！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　アタラモ王が声を低くして言った。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「<ruby rubyText="とら">虎</ruby><ruby rubyText="おう">王</ruby>を<ruby rubyText="そそのか">唆</ruby>し、カレヴァーラを<ruby rubyText="たお">倒</ruby>してギムの国を我がものとするとは、見事なまでの悪党よのう？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「何が言いたい？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「お前の野望はこの程度で満足するものではあるまい？</sentence>
<sentence>　次の望みは何だ？</sentence>
<sentence>　エルの国を手に入れることか？</sentence>
<sentence>　それともカヤの国か？</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">　フフフ…そのような小国、すでに手に入れたも同じのお前にはどうでも良いものだな」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「！</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">…」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　アタラモ王は窓の木戸を閉め、ゆっくりと<ruby rubyText="やみ">闇</ruby>の<ruby rubyText="メシア">救世主</ruby>の前の<ruby rubyText="いす">椅子</ruby>に近づいて腰を下ろした。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「余の望みが何かを知っていると申すのか？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「フフフ…」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「答えよ！</sentence>
<sentence>　余が何を望んでおるのか？」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「あらゆる富、永遠の命、この世で持てるすべての力…というところか」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「この世に生まれ出でし者であれば持つ、当り前の望みではないか！</sentence>
<sentence>　そう思わぬか？」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「フフフ…当り前のな」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「そうだ！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「<ruby rubyText="あく">悪</ruby><ruby rubyText="ま">魔</ruby>に<ruby rubyText="たましい">魂</ruby>を売り、天上界までも支配しようとするのが当り前の望みか…」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　皮肉な笑みが闇の救世主の口元に<ruby rubyText="う">浮</ruby>かんだ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「<ruby rubyText="たわ">戯</ruby>けたことを申すな！</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">　天上界などとおそれ多い」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「だが、その野望もメイサがいなくては砂で<ruby rubyText="か">描</ruby>いた絵も同じ…。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">風のひと<ruby rubyText="ふ">吹</ruby>きで消えてしまう」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「知っているのか、メイサの居所を？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「メイサをギムの国より連れ出したのは私だ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「なに？</sentence>
<sentence>　では、今どこにいる？」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「ノアの国、ラグナマリアの元だ！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「なんだと！？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　小さな体が飛び上がるようにして、アタラモ王は<ruby rubyText="いす">椅子</ruby>から立った。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「<ruby rubyText="ざ">戯</ruby>れ<ruby rubyText="ごと">言</ruby>を申すと<ruby rubyText="ため">為</ruby>にならんぞ！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　アタラモ王の額から<ruby rubyText="あせ">汗</ruby>が流れ落ち、大きく開かれた眼には<ruby rubyText="いか">怒</ruby>りと<ruby rubyText="おそ">恐</ruby>れの火が見えた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「この地上界を支配するに、最も<ruby rubyText="しょう">障</ruby><ruby rubyText="がい">害</ruby>となる者の手にメイサはある」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「お、おのれ！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「どうする『<ruby rubyText="ザール・エ・ザール">王の中の王</ruby>』よ？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　アタラモ王は、<ruby rubyText="やみ">闇</ruby>の<ruby rubyText="メシア">救世主</ruby>の眼を見つめたまま、呼吸が落ち着くのを待って言った。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「余の元へメイサを連れて来れば望みのものを取らすぞ！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「『ファラの星』を！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「！</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">…」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　アタラモ王の呼吸が<ruby rubyText="いっ">一</ruby><ruby rubyText="しゅん">瞬</ruby>止まった。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「ラグナマリアに仕える者か？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「<ruby rubyText="だれ">誰</ruby>に仕える者でもない…。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">お前にもな」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「ならばメイサを連れて来い！</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">　そのうえで…」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　今度はアタラモ王の<ruby rubyText="ほお">頰</ruby>に笑みが<ruby rubyText="う">浮</ruby>かんだ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「『ノアの星』を手に入れる手助けをせい！</sentence>
<sentence>　その礼としてそちにも『力』を<ruby rubyText="あた">与</ruby>えよう！」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「力？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「そうだ！</sentence>
<sentence>　<ruby rubyText="よ">余</ruby>と共に三つの世界を支配する『力』だ！」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「フフフ…悪い話ではないな」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「であろう？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「だが、同じことをラグナマリアからも言われている」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「なに？</sentence>
<sentence>　おのれ、あの<ruby rubyText="ま">魔</ruby><ruby rubyText="じょ">女</ruby>が！」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「ラグナマリアの持つ『ノアの星』、お前が持つ『ファラの星』と…、ふたつだけでは用を足すまい？</sentence>
<sentence>　あとひとつ、『ギムの星』はどうする？」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「！</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">…」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「ギムの国のどこからも見つからなかったのだろう？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「ギムの国はこの余が落としたのだ！</sentence>
<sentence>　『ギムの星』は余のもの！</sentence>
<sentence>　ラグナマリアに取られてなるか！」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「ラグナマリアからの<ruby rubyText="こと">言</ruby><ruby rubyText="づて">伝</ruby>だ。</sentence>
<sentence>メイサが欲しくば『ファラの星』を持って、バードム海に<ruby rubyText="う">浮</ruby>かぶ『<ruby rubyText="らん">蘭</ruby>の島』まで来い！」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「蘭の島？</sentence>
<sentence>…。</sentence>
<sentence>待て<sampling type="end" />！」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
</article>
</sample>
